{"tid":1177733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西貢男留遺書 獨立屋天台長褲吊頸亡","createTime":"2019-05-30T02:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T03:15:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d6883b1d66847e8fad65b32290ad5bb8b3369696","tid":1177733,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:26:56.000Z","msg":"西貢一名54歲男子留下遺書，於大網仔路近大環村一獨立屋內，以長褲吊頸死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚8時04分接獲途人報案，指懷疑有人於大環村一獨立屋暈倒。警員接報到場，發現事主於天台一房間以長褲上吊，當場被證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方於現場檢獲遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E7%95%99%E9%81%BA%E6%9B%B8-%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%B1%8B%E5%A4%A9%E5%8F%B0%E9%95%B7%E8%A4%B2%E5%90%8A%E9%A0%B8%E4%BA%A1-000100248.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B2%25A2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E7%2595%2599%25E9%2581%25BA%25E6%259B%25B8-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A4%25B2%25E5%2590%258A%25E9%25A0%25B8%25E4%25BA%25A1-000100248.html&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuicjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=5e606126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E7%95%99%E9%81%BA%E6%9B%B8-%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%B1%8B%E5%A4%A9%E5%8F%B0%E9%95%B7%E8%A4%B2%E5%90%8A%E9%A0%B8%E4%BA%A1-000100248.html</a>"},{"pid":"b925b3af4cae97037a55175d1affa7917ec488e3","tid":1177733,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:30:30.000Z","msg":"天堂冇共產黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f2f69862dbc812fbde04de12a3170dd0b78b15","tid":1177733,"uid":9526,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯天文台台長吊頸亡"},{"pid":"3ee6fc3fa7341b231dff7752d47e7848b940cb13","tid":1177733,"uid":46373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19f2f69862dbc812fbde04de12